curam.common.util.xml.dom

Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Content
      • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Attribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomWrapper

    public class Attribute
extends Content
    An Attribute defines an XML attribute. An attribute may have a name, an optional namespace and a value. This implementation wraps a dom4j Attribute.
